			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2223573">
									

<p>And here&#8230; we&#8230; go.</p>
<p>A couple extra points for the helpful few who saw this draft beforehand and helped proofread it. <strong>No need to read this if you didn't see the draft version.</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The traditional SCP format may be only used once per entry.</li>
<li>No collaborations. You can share ideas and help brainstorm, but one writer per entry. (If you help each other with minor things that's fine.)</li>
<li>The contest submission period has been shortened; it's now two weeks long. The start date is the same, however.</li>
<li>Some Series 2 SCPs are okay to use for the central concept. This is because we got mixed up and forgot that Series 2 started in the middle of 2011.</li>
</ul>

