<p>Three distinct documents means that if you use the SCP format, you also need at least two other tabs. You can write an experiment log, or a tale, or an MC&amp;D catalog &#8212; whatever you want, really, as long as each document has substance. The rule's in place to stop people from just rewriting an SCP in the SCP format.</p>

